@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_subtyn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((tmp - (tmp + 0.87 - v1 + 0.00)))
    v2 = wp.abs(v0)
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v1 + 0.39 / v2 + 0.67)))
    v2 = 0.44
    data[tid] = v0
